{"includedIn":[],"title":"Rififi","slug":"rififi","synopsis":"This superbly gritty underworld thriller was French director Jules Dassin's last stab at a comeback after being hounded across Europe by McCarthyist America. For 30 wordless minutes four veteran criminals expertly slip into a Paris jewellery shop and make off with 240 million francs' worth of ice. There's no fancy sensors that can read the combination number, no lasers to be overcome with hi-tech nightsights or all-seeing closed circuit televisions to disable. Instead, the gang unfurl a brolly after drilling a hole above to catch the falling plaster. Then, using an old-fashioned drill, they cut a disc out of a back of the safe and grab the moulah. One of the most engrossing sequences you'll see in any movie.","shortSynopsis":"Belting crime classic about four men planning the perfect heist, but something always goes wrong.","mediumSynopsis":"Mismatched thieves plot to swipe a fortune in gems from a jewellers - but their chances of success seem small. French drama, starring Jean Servais.","guidanceText":"sexual content, strong language, violent scenes","actors":[{"name":"Carl MÃ¶hner","slug":"carl-mohner","rel":"person","id":"ffac9c1c-87d1-428d-8c20-9146c9c236c3","links":[{"rel":"search","href":"https://www.skystore.com/api/web/v2/catalog/assets/search/advanced/carl-mohner?actor=Carl+M%C3%B6hner","method":"GET","needsAuthentication":false},{"rel":"person","href":"https://www.skystore.com/api/web/v2/catalog/assets/actor/ffac9c1c-87d1-428d-8c20-9146c9c236c3/carl-mohner","method":"GET","needsAuthentication":false}]},{"name":"Jean Servais","slug":"jean-servais","rel":"person","id":"ead30da9-bba6-458a-a2ec-81bd3f80787a","links":[{"rel":"search","href":"https://www.skystore.com/api/web/v2/catalog/assets/search/advanced/jean-servais?actor=Jean+Servais","method":"GET","needsAuthentication":false},{"rel":"person","href":"https://www.skystore.com/api/web/v2/catalog/assets/actor/ead30da9-bba6-458a-a2ec-81bd3f80787a/je